‘He’s very busy in Grozny,’ said Mr De 
Caumont, referring to the capital of Chechnya, where Depardieu and Miss 
Hurley are working.

Mr De Caumont said Depardieu 'asked me to represent him in court where he wants to be judged, as he always said.'

